show.description: “My birth is my fatal accident”. Idhu JNU student Rohit Vemula ezhudiya suicide note. Oru pakkam technology, development nu India valarchi paadhai la ponaalum, innum caste based discriminations ah thodarchiya namma makkal sandhichuttu dhan irukaanga. Adhanaala pona pala uyirgal la Rohit’um oruthar. JNU, IITs madhiri prestigious institutions la Underprivileged students face panra issues ah pathiyum, adhukku edhir ah poraadiya voices pathiyum therinjuka kelunga “The Ferment - Youth Unrest In India” only on Kuku FM
